{"Id":644996,"Title":"永思堂诗","Dynasty":"明","Author":"杨士奇","Context":"南山之木，厥有本根。浩浩川流，则亦有原。凡世之氓，孰无父母。生我育我，忧勤是保。我疾在躬，父母怦怦。我躬既平，父母载宁。我事父母，千载未足。云胡一朝，去我不复。林栖者乌，则有反哺。哀哉小子，欲养无所。岂无厚禄，岂无华缨。我无父母，于谁为荣。靡旦靡夕，孔怀弗忘。父兮母兮，如睹羹墙。居则以思，行则以思。音容慌焉，梦寐对之。父天母地，覆载同德。哀哀我心，何穷何极。先哲有训，立身忠君。我惇用之，敢怠于勤。无敢怠勤，恒恭敬止。终焉永怀，悠悠曷已。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"","Status":1,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"03889ef6e9487ff5239d9e69a4aec1af","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":7275938,"Sentence":"南山之木，厥有本根。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"nā shān zhī mù ，jué yǒu běn gēn ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275939,"Sentence":"浩浩川流，则亦有原。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hào hào chuān lǐu ，zé yì yǒu yuán ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275940,"Sentence":"凡世之氓，孰无父母。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"fán shì zhī máng ，shú mó fǔ mǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":2,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275941,"Sentence":"生我育我，忧勤是保。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shēng wǒ yō wǒ ，yōu qǐn shì bǎo ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275942,"Sentence":"我疾在躬，父母怦怦。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ jǐ zài gōng ，fǔ mǔ pēng pēng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275943,"Sentence":"我躬既平，父母载宁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ gōng jì pǐng ，fǔ mǔ zǎi nǐng ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275944,"Sentence":"我事父母，千载未足。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"wǒ shì fǔ mǔ ，qiān zǎi wèi zú ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":6,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275945,"Sentence":"云胡一朝，去我不复。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"yún hú yī cháo ，qù wǒ bú fù ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"明"},{"Id":7275946,"Sentence":"林栖者乌，则有反哺。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"lǐn qī zhě wū ，zé yǒu fǎn bǔ ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort